<subSubSection id="EBBF6528FF9B9E6E0BBEFEBB993B06A8" pageId="8" pageNumber="257" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="A31A36A3FF9B9E6E0BBEFEBB993B06A8" blockId="8.[151,1437,151,645]" pageId="8" pageNumber="257">
<emphasis id="91D1EAB1FF9B9E6E0BBEFEBB9A0B0661" bold="true" box="[199,335,330,356]" pageId="8" pageNumber="257">Comments.</emphasis>
The new species was found in the riverbed (sand bottom), one meter deep in the dry season. The river, in the sector where the new species was collected, has approximately five meters width; it is surrounded by pasture, almost without riparian vegetation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="EBBF6528FF9B9E6E0BBEFE469E0B06F0" pageId="8" pageNumber="257" type="etymology">
